Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻过所有的杂志也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 与我相称的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都无法 讨得你的欢心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉让你失望了 对不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是与我紧紧地缠绕的话不行哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  别用那种冷冷的眼神望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我照着自己的步调去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我很快就会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰这样不稳的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的又有什么不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此还是得向前迈进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  一点也不成问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.24,0:21:44.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.75,0:21:49.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  这就是爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.21,0:21:55.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手寻找温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.47,0:22:01.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  奇迹也一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.81,0:22:14.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有爱 就绝对有具体的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.65,0:22:25.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 现在 在我手中 有诞生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.42,0:22:33.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神饱满  也不能   太过勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.80,0:22:38.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.22,0:22:49.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起来  培育茁壮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.17,0:00:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.14,0:00:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞台是环状线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.68,0:00:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件和电车可都没有结束的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.38,0:00:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默的环状线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.63,0:02:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔真是个麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚完成一件工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我喝一杯啤酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么完成一件工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.77,0:02:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是来拿忘记在委托人那里的信封而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.71,0:02:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是星期日 没有人上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.73,0:02:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天人真少啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为星期日的晚上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近是办公大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时是因为上班所以人比较多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的好辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 给你们添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是迷糊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早你一年进来的清美比你机灵多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 清美那家伙赶着回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什么急事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是赶去约会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是星期日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都是某个人的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.27,0:03:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我们要星期日都出来加班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会好好补偿你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每次都这样讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要这么责备她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由纪子也不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.61,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又这样袒护新人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样害我变成坏人角色了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样讲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个不要再吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(二号站台电车即将进站)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买罐果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车已经来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先上车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由纪子不知道有没有坐上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩总是喜欢慢吞吞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.78,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们假装不认识爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 由纪子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过果汁却洒了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.92,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是胡涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由纪子 你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美小姐不是早就回去了吗？ 为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她睡得很沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.88,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么她就在这环状线绕了一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她一定是很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来了 清美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有脉搏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你们是认识的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是侦探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有名的....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.08,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个名人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳垂上好像被什么东西刺过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这只耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点瘀青的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 这个人的耳朵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只耳朵的颜色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是中毒的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有可能是被杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰 去找车长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条痕迹是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警方来之前请不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你们也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要触摸死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把车上的乘客名字、电话和地址都记下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.16,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推定时间是下午六点半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现尸体是在七点半过后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个环状线绕一圈大概是一个小时十分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真的是在电车里面死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说被害者在上车之后马上就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.16,0:07:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后坐着环状线绕了一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么死因呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.67,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是被涂有剧毒的针之类的东西刺到耳朵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.50,0:07:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它也没有看到挣扎或者是打斗的迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.43,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是被害者的皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个皮包好像一开始就是打开着的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要多嘴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.17,0:07:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人有可能从皮包中拿走了什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 被害者的钱包还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面也不像被人动过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就去问那三个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会知道些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.99,0:08:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.97,0:08:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想确认一下死者的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.94,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩看到这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像失了魂的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能怪她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先请你们两人协助调查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 不要在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.17,0:08:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到那边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…还好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美一直会带的东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会全部知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过征二也许会知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很想和她交朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.51,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还送过礼物给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.54,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和被害者正在交往吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 每次都被她拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.03,0:09:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就有那种想报仇的动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静香 你怎么可以这样讲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.18,0:09:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们平时都很要好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天发生了那件事 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说　因为工作关系你们回到公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来只有桥本清美小姐一个人先回去了 对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期日 还有工作要做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.14,0:09:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是做广告美术设计的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我昨天做错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以害大家今天都要来上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最后看到清美小姐是什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二番街车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们送她到车站去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候清美小姐有什么异状吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是在检票口分开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有什么不同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.97,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是下午六点三十分左右的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.67,0:10:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后在发现已经死亡的清美之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.19,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三人都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.26,0:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美小姐有没有和人结怨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才的对话中得知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.11,0:10:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不被清美小姐理睬的你是最有可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由纪子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是因为爱人被抢走所以很恨她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我并没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且静香你也讲过你的作品被她盗用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 大家都有杀人动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推定时间是下午六点半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们在车站分手的时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是在那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.05,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的一直都在一起吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个一起吃饭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们平时都去同一家餐厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话去问问看就可以知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有不在场证明的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以确定他们不是嫌犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是电车之狼的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经登记好所有乘客的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在里面可以找到凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被害者的皮包是打开着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便进行指纹测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人为什么要在电车中杀害她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是刺耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被压过痕迹的耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为是电车之狼的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.10,0:11:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.27,0:11:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道清美小姐为什么会被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MD播放器还有耳罩型耳机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的MD盘旁边都有贴上贴纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是MD的贴纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一张正面贴上了贴纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.12,0:12:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个颜色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪我觉得有什么地方很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以在有不在场证明的情况下杀了清美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人一定是那个人没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我推理正确的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人应该就是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过证据却不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的东西还没检查完吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概已经检查完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么可能从她的皮包里偷走什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.34,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡乱给人定罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了 静香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是警部先生他们的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.86,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以胡闹啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 征二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 反正我很容易出汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以外出都会多带一件衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.93,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去我的行李中拿更换的衣服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可以乱动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向那个哥哥说对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个死去的清美小姐和大家都相处得很不错吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然刚才一时气愤说大家都很恨清美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过并不是真的很恨她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.29,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.09,0:14:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天由纪子将清美的MD播放器掉到地上摔坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.23,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美那家伙一点都没生气 就这样原谅她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是由纪子和清美的关系最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为男朋友被抢她们会起争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你讲这些好像还太早了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美小姐和我们一样是从二番街车站上车的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过清美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是坐在前面第二节车厢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常会在检票口那里上车吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然特意往前走到第二节车厢上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都觉得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美下车的车站出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好对准第二节车厢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每次和她一起回去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要走到第二节车厢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说清美小姐会在第二节车厢上车的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.44,0:15:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们三人早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的谜底都解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 携带品全部都调查过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 打扰了你们这么多的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以拿回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么问题的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候请你们再次合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还不能回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个姿势是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人并不是电车之狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他们三人其中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说犯人就在我们之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.03,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶器也是在你们的东西手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人都有不在场证明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人正在一起吃饭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.63,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样也有机会可以杀害清美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.32,0:16:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 知道清美小姐会先走的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车站一边送她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边确认清美小姐上车的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测已经死亡的她再度回到这个车站的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.51,0:16:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再和大家一起吃饭制造不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.72,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从回到车站的死者身上把凶器给回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的凶器到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.46,0:16:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不懂吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放在耳朵上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来也不会是很奇怪的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在耳机上面放上毒药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说犯人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森由纪子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.94,0:16:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将清美小姐的MD播放器给弄坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把自己的借给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预先在耳机上面涂上毒药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.46,0:17:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你说要去买果汁而从前面的车厢上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把凶器给回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.06,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美小姐每次回家都会坐到第二节车厢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点由纪子知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要知道位置的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.17,0:17:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回收凶器并不需要花很多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是耳机线因为被清美小姐压住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有硬把它扯下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果耳机就断掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳机的确断了一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的手上留有耳机线的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.81,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且死者的耳朵好像被压过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都证明她戴过耳机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是去买了一瓶果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有做那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看到同事的尸体的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却去帮她拉领子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.53,0:18:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是因为拉耳机的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心把领子拉竖起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本只想拿走凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.68,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让尸体就这样摆在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征二先生他们从后面的车厢走了过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就在那里与大家一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装发现清美小姐的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们一起留在现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.88,0:18:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说被害者是自己将毒刺进自己的耳朵里面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.26,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么要在电车里面呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.28,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路线在星期日的晚上乘客就会变少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二节车厢差不多都没人坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.31,0:18:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样要制造不在场证明、回收凶器是最好的地点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.76,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且其它车辆上有其他乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很容易被误认是电车之狼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就故意在工作上出错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都在星期日一起出来工作的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据呢 你有证据吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面一点类似针的东西都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那只针大概是利用手帕将它给拔掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为手帕上面还残留着耳机的棉花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直坐在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和大家在一起的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在确认遗物的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过不太舒服而留下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.73,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拿掉针的话 必须单独行动才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以把手帕借给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.89,0:19:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一只很小的针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就不知道丢到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只是推测而没有证据吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.86,0:19:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 证据就在MD播放器里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.24,0:19:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是说指纹的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友当然会有我的指纹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我没借给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.81,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以从播放器里面把MD盘给拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.61,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 由纪子 清美留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没借给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才好像是这样讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有借过给她的MD盘上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.23,0:20:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何会有今天的日期的留言信息呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是从遗物中的圆珠笔写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些字的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.57,0:20:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遗物里面的圆珠笔的颜色一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.04,0:20:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清美小姐给你的留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.93,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己根本没想过你会杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是因为受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把我的男朋友给抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是他的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.86,0:21:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想清美才会这么急着回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才会想选择今天去杀死她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.13,0:22:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她是从哪里得到毒药的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.35,0:23:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在南美用在吹箭上面 即死的毒药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.44,0:23:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天去旅行的时候发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.71,0:23:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就把它涂在小针上面放到耳机里面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹箭的毒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.44,0:23:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个毒可花了我们不少时间调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.56,0:23:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利 如果没有你的名推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.73,0:23:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也许无法解开这个谜底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.26,0:23:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹箭的毒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.09,0:23:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想大概就是那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.63,0:23:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你一早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.41,0:23:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是毛利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.43,0:23:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是我的麻醉枪被叔叔发现了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.19,0:23:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 报应出现了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.52,0:23:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.57,0:23:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.16,0:24:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚是碰不到栏杆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.83,0:24:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自杀没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.88,0:24:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 这是被人杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.16,0:24:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.63,0:24:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的五重塔传说(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.18,0:24:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.62,0:24:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回可是围绕着恐怖传说的五重塔
